{"tid":1017994,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【突發】廢老居然叫護士……","createTime":"2019-02-12T01:09:31.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-12T05:32:46.000Z","uid":225464,"like":19,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"3b6af5bf572e91aedb7891fbd232cb637f95bd26","tid":1017994,"uid":225464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:09:31.000Z","msg":"稱孫兒便便有酸味　婆婆求證護士︰你聞唔到就試吓<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://bit.ly/2MZZXSW\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2MZZXSW&d=hKO5vKCyTOC8%2FV9T1xBu1%2FUf%2F0pSCBsIIvLsnv1ZXiY%3D&h=20fb5203\" target=\"_blank\">https://bit.ly/2MZZXSW</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20190212/photo/bkn-20190212081503795-0212_00822_001_01p.jpg?20190212081850\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20190212%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20190212081503795-0212_00822_001_01p.jpg%3F20190212081850&h=e1fb772b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n會唔會成間診所都有陣味？<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n生病當然要看醫生。惟近日有愛孫心切的婆婆，拿着已使用過的嬰兒尿片闖入診所，竟然為了讓姑娘幫手「試味」？<br />\n<br />\n有護士星期一（11日）在其Facebook專頁「診所低能奇觀」分享奇怪經歷，指有日一位婆婆走入其任職的診所，表明自己不是來看醫生，而是想「借你個人嚟用吓」。她深感有異而斷然拒絕。<br />\n<br />\n未料婆婆從手袋中拿出前一天孫兒使用過的尿片，聲稱自己「隔住條片都聞到啲屎酸」，但其兒子及媳婦卻聞不出來，心感委屈，決定找護士幫忙「認證」︰「你隊個頭埋嚟呀，我畀你聞呀」。<br />\n<br />\n她頓時大驚，解釋若小朋友不舒服，應直接看醫生，又以長期鼻敏感及鼻塞為由推搪。婆婆一臉茫然地說︰「咁&hellip;你食唔食到味㗎」、「冇要你食呀，試吓味咋嘛，聞唔到咪試吓酸唔酸」。<br />\n<br />\n為免被迫試味，她只好敷衍表示隔夜會變味。婆婆深受「啟發」︰「咁下次我係咪應該即刻試咗先呀。」她默不作聲，婆婆繼續說道︰「下次我叫佢哋試，佢哋就知道真係酸㗎啦，應該唔會再話係我問題啦！」方才開心地離開診所。<br />\n<br />\n該護士無奈感慨︰「勞保包唔包食屎引起嘅身體不適㗎醫生」、「大佬你一嘢就逼人食屎，邊個敢話係你問題呀」。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民直言惡心︰「好玩唔玩，玩屎」、「黐線㗎！份工唔包食屎㗎」。有人則笑指︰「就嚟抱孫都要考牌」、「護士真係最危險嘅職業」。"},{"pid":"3db0d320202fc749520af24cc289598a0a84b034","tid":1017994,"uid":20602,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:16:24.000Z","msg":"個page 出名作故仔"},{"pid":"2369ab6dca561daf65757ae43797637a080d61a0","tid":1017994,"uid":90820,"like":29,"dislike":1,"score":28,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:46:24.000Z","msg":"呢個page好撚假<br />\n日日都咁多奇奇怪怪嘅病人咩<br />\n又唔見其他姑娘撞到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"285fc1f66a1410b1d8541eb3a940d61623824402","tid":1017994,"uid":18251,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T01:49:23.000Z","msg":"佢以為睇中醫？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8027acd1194cef6f9246f3e690d7c7d0c8f592b8","tid":1017994,"uid":280,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T02:23:01.000Z","msg":"呀婆係咪有病 其實個屎片係佢自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/clown4.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇好老人家啦屌"},{"pid":"3852c008402cef5fb4d98d1ce581d1eb02f1a57d","tid":1017994,"uid":114186,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:04:58.000Z","msg":"診所嗰d唔係護士<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"42473e4102a1ec9b2af6a678cd4b58fb911ae846","tid":1017994,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:09:24.000Z","msg":"講故台來<br />\n寫埋甜故都仲得"},{"pid":"f8820233bea28e2f536eda14ed345425edb1e3d5","tid":1017994,"uid":113626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:10:33.000Z","msg":"個title同連登仔心諗既完全唔同 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2eb5a87c004011f60b6f0528807565eef8ba645d","tid":1017994,"uid":78349,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:15:28.000Z","msg":"原來唔係得我一個覺得個珍寶豬吹水<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 屌 吹得就吹<br />\n利申 護士 同時有做過診所助護"},{"pid":"55b7ecbb7c3ce5b7a846d0751915f5dc72e788c1","tid":1017994,"uid":402,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:16:30.000Z","msg":"假野"},{"pid":"c3da95931215186702da458b8ff98765bb04bd50","tid":1017994,"uid":183722,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-12T04:18:55.000Z","msg":"個婆婆係咪demen<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"898bcfe0fa977826a04364dc8e0d